Class GridParametersManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.tessilab.oss.hypop.parameters.managers.ParametersManager
      • io.tessilab.oss.hypop.parameters.managers.GridParametersManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    io.tessilab.oss.openutils.designpatterns.observer.ParametrizedObserver<ProcessResult>

    public class GridParametersManager
extends ParametersManager
    The ParametersManager who retrives the parameters in order to performm a grid search ( combination of all the possible values of all the possible parameters)

    (For more details, see the Grid Search paragraph here : https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hyperparameter_optimization )

    Author:
    Andres BEL ALONSO
